   sql:select g.*,um.name username,s.name schoolname,t.name tagname from goods g left join tags t on t.id=g.tag left join users u on u.id =g.uid left join users_msg um on um.id=u.mid left join school s on um.school=s.id where g.name like '%``%' or s.name like '%``%' or um.name like '%``%' or t.name like '%``%'
